Class AttributeMapping

  • java.lang.Object
    • oracle.adfmf.util.XmlAnyDefinition
      • oracle.ateam.sample.mobile.v2.persistence.metadata.AttributeMapping
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    oracle.adfmf.metadata.Node, oracle.adfmf.util.KXmlUtil.KXmlParsableElement
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AttributeMappingDirect, AttributeMappingOneToMany, AttributeMappingOneToOne

    public abstract class AttributeMapping
extends oracle.adfmf.util.XmlAnyDefinition
    Superclass of all attribute mapping classes. Returns common information that all attribute mappings provide. The information is read from the TopLink XML mapping file as configured in mobile-persistence-config.properties
